Comment.val: Batchprogramma van de nieuwe versie van de FX-vervalkalender.

SQL_STMT_U.val:
(select distinct fx.fx_einddatum, fx.fx_rel1_a_rek2_mntst as munt, '1' as ms, fx.fx_rel1, cl.cl_rapportage_naam, fx.fx_contractnummer, fx.fx_spot, fx.fx_ingangsdatum, fx.fx_adviseur_invoer, fx.fx_indicatie, fx.fx_bedrag as bedrag, cl.cl_clientgroep, cl.cl_relatie_categorie, cl.cl_nummer, cl.cl_adviseur, cl.cl_adviseur_2, cl.cl_afdelingadviseur from FX_CONTRACTEN fx, CLIENTEN cl where fx.fx_rel1 = cl.cl_nummer and ((~11 = 0) or (~11 = 1 and fx.fx_spot = 1) or (~11 = 2 and fx.fx_spot = 2)) and fx.fx_actueel = 1 and cl.cl_clientgroep between ~1 and ~2 and cl.cl_relatie_categorie between ~3 and ~4 and cl.cl_adviseur between ~5 and ~6 and fx.fx_einddatum between ~7 and ~8 and fx.fx_rel1 between ~9 and ~10 and ( ~12 = 0 or exists ( select 1 from WERKBESTAND wk where wk.wk_terminal = ~13 and wk.wk_soort = ~14 and cl.cl_nummer = to_number ( wk.wk_categorie_1 ) )) )
union all
(select distinct fx.fx_einddatum, fx.fx_rel1_v_rek2_mntst as munt, '2' as ms, fx.fx_rel1, cl.cl_rapportage_naam, fx.fx_contractnummer, fx.fx_spot, fx.fx_ingangsdatum, fx.fx_adviseur_invoer, fx.fx_indicatie, fx.fx_bedrag_vv2 as bedrag, cl.cl_clientgroep, cl.cl_relatie_categorie, cl.cl_nummer, cl.cl_adviseur, cl.cl_adviseur_2, cl.cl_afdelingadviseur from FX_CONTRACTEN fx, CLIENTEN cl where fx.fx_rel1 = cl.cl_nummer and ((~11 = 0) or (~11 = 1 and fx.fx_spot = 1) or (~11 = 2 and fx.fx_spot = 2)) and fx.fx_actueel = 1 and cl.cl_clientgroep between ~1 and ~2 and cl.cl_relatie_categorie between ~3 and ~4 and cl.cl_adviseur between ~5 and ~6 and fx.fx_einddatum between ~7 and ~8 and fx.fx_rel1 between ~9 and ~10 and ( ~12 = 0 or exists ( select 1 from WERKBESTAND wk where wk.wk_terminal = ~13 and wk.wk_soort = ~14 and cl.cl_nummer = to_number ( wk.wk_categorie_1 ) )) )
order by 1,2,4
